  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the antinflammatory and endothelial progenitor cell
      (EPC) mobilizing effect of Ramipril and Telmisartan in patients presenting with acute
      coronary syndrome
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
